 and interesting. And I found almost no interview with him to get at that depth. I was very hopeful

1:21:48.240 --> 1:21:56.400
 for the Oliver Stone documentary with him and to me, because I deeply respect Oliver Stone

1:21:56.400 --> 1:22:01.120
 as a filmmaker in general, but it was a complete failure in my eyes, that interview.

1:22:05.680 --> 1:22:13.200
 I suppose you could toss it up to a language barrier, but a complete lack of diving deep

